#13-feb-2021
1) Planning to use react-native owing to below reasons:
  a) Not planning to have very complex features
  b) May need a web-app
  c) Not as bad in computation extensiveness as hybrid app, need to run a lot of test-cases
  d) Has integration with java sdk too: https://reactnative.dev/docs/native-modules-android
  
2) Firebase will be adopted for following use-cases:
  a) For normal DB operations
  b) Authentication and authorization
